 class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">PMS 321U</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Teal</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Puff Additive</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/F/3/F30ED0177A55B28A37F92EE0100568FD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">PMS Cool Grey #5 U</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Cool Gray #5</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Puff Additive</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/3/5/35EB0F656F3D5E59201BFC2759D57296.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">PMS Match</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">PMS Color Match</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">PMS imprint colors other than standard imprint colors listed can be matched for an additional charge per color as below. \nPMS matches can only be guaranteed on White products.  Imprint colors on non-white products will not be exact due to the nature of the process.</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$25.00 each</p></div></div>\n</details>\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Additional Charges</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">The below charges represent a GENERAL list and some charges may vary or not even be an option on certain products. Contact factory to be sure.</p><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Additional Charges</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Converting Artwork to Vector Format</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Art submitted in non-vector format will incur an art charge to convert to vector format.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Please add 24 hours to order's production time to allow for art conversion.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$50.00 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Additional Charges</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Less Than Catalog Minimum</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;A charge to any order for less than the catalog minimum&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Less than minimum orders are only available on items that are available 24 Hour Service. Items that are not applicable for 24-hour service have a firm catalog minimum.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$50.00 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Additional Charges</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Mixing Imprint Colors</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Mixing imprint ink colors on the same item within an order will incur a charge for each imprint color change.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$25.00 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Additional Charges</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Mixing Product Colors</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Splitting an order across two product colors is free of charge.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Every additional item color past two, will incur a charge&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$5.00 each</p></div></div>\n</details>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500 mt-4\">Final quote may reflect selected options, proofs, rush, or freight beyond list pricing.</p>\n</div>","salesToolsHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p><strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">Pitch this SKU</strong> — FoamZone Collapsible Can Cooler. Lead with use case (uniforms, retail, teams, recognition), then minimums and timeline. Reference included services from “Price includes” in the Description tab when present (e.g. setup, virtual proof, shipping offers).</p>\n<ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-2\">\n<li>Quote style <span class=\"font-mono text-neutral-900\">FZCC</span> on proposals and POs.</li>\n<li>Offer virtual proofs and artwork checks before production.</li>\n<li>Cross-sell with hats, bags, or jackets for kit programs.</li>\n<li>For decoration and imprint methods, follow supplier notes in the Description tab.</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500\">Approved partners can request internal sell sheets, comparison matrices, and margin guidance from the A Design Line team.</p>\n</div>","inventoryHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p>Merchandise is <strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">typically sourced to order</strong>. Stock and availability may vary by supplier and season.</p>\n<p>Supplier-stated production window: <strong>3 days</strong> (not including transit).</p>\n<p>Contact the studio for <strong>rush</strong> feasibility, <strong>split shipments</strong>, or <strong>multi-location</strong> drops before placing large orders.</p>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500\">Minimum order quantity: <strong class=\"text-neutral-800\">100</strong> units (per catalog line).</p>\n</div>"}